Done. Commit `4a768bf` — `feat(cli): v0.2 workflow run onboard`.

## What was implemented

**New file**: `src/cli/workflow.rs` — 292 lines
- `run()` dispatcher matching `"onboard"` to `run_onboard()`, `"capture"` → v0.3+ error, unknown → error
- `run_onboard()` — checks `.enjoyknowledge/` exists, reads AGENTS.md, locates POSITIONING/DESIGN-PHILOSOPHY/DESIGN files, collects critical gotchas (severity 4–5) and active decisions, counts total knowledge files
- `OnboardOutput`, `GotchaEntry`, `DecisionEntry` structs
- Human-readable output via `print_onboard_output()`

**Modified files**:
- `src/cli/args.rs` — added `Workflow { workflow: String }` variant after `Export`
- `src/cli/mod.rs` — added `pub mod workflow;`
- `src/main.rs` — added `Command::Workflow` dispatch branch
- `src/format/frontmatter.rs` — added `severity: Option<u8>` and `status: Option<String>` fields
- `src/cli/export.rs` — fixed pre-existing `anyhow::Error::contains()` compilation errors (3 places) + `doc_markdown` lint

**New test file**: `tests/cmd/workflow-onboard.trycmd`

